Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:23.23,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}黑夜初降  波瀾暗湧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:25.57,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}令人興奮難抑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:30.20,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}七色音符  永劫綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:31.45,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}心中忐忑不安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:35.41,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}魔錘的烙印  現於暗礁之上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:37.50,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}玩夠了沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:41.33,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}循於愛之真理  極光閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:42.96,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}差不多行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:48.63,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我們終將合二為一  翱翔於天際
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:54.31,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}浮華如焰火  喧囂過後終將凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:59.85,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}刹那之間…迸發光芒萬丈！！
