Comment: 0,0:00:00.12,0:00:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進入高二已經兩個月了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熟悉了新班級  也習慣了身為前輩的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待著我們的  便是這一學年…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是整個高中歲月最重要的活動之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修學旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.18,0:00:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝了  樟葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且對我來說  這也是個特別的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花  準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開門了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噓  當心被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來沒有驚動到黑暗的耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還是要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發出太大的聲響會擾得四鄰不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好意思說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你戴這個東西幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛剛結束喚醒暗炎龍的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上這個能強化邪王真眼的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以獲得洞察隔絕世界的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還很帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了快收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.78,0:01:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了快收拾  收拾完了去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是要前往黑暗世界  準備如此周密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還是精簡過了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得還背著個包包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  你是指
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨身行李隨身帶嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36}注：手に持つだけに手荷物。冷笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒玩夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好笑嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  大家集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人奔赴戰場期間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓凸守成為結社的守護神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凸守
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅途愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天打扮得挺精神的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修學旅行嘛  充滿了未知的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:04:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我來宣佈每個小組的娛樂節目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了去衛生間以外  不准去其他車廂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手機也是  禁止通話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是音速級
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒  其實還沒那麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但邪王真眼已經洞察了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和去年回她老家的時候已經很不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆還是那麼親密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別亂拍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦  反正你們也在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼在交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心不會給別人看的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候列印出來給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來一小時是自由活動時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩點在這裡集合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡看起來好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被黑暗守護聖人幽禁的龍之靈魂  就沉睡在這座宮殿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此處即是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Dark  Draconian's  Saint  Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑龍人聖殿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別亂起名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下我要躲開黑暗的耳目潛入此處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太也一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論何時都要警惕黑暗耳目的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還專門把這個帶過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰準備必須周全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來這玩意你很喜歡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  小鳥游同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你戴的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是老樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不如在這裡給你跟富樫君來個合影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別害羞嘛  這可是修學旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:06:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快靠近點  跟男朋友留下點美好回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  富樫你在這
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們組的計劃表在你這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這在這
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事幹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去精神活動會停止的  真的要Death了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  難道說那是主人的使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凸守在這呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草蔭佈滿捕蠅草…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36}注：ハエトリソウが生えとる。冷笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午睡對決一役以來  你似乎更加熱衷於午睡事業了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小凸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於從幻夢世界中回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡現在已經是停滯領域了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們必須快快逃離  向別處進擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往哪裡進擊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  既然這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印著黑暗力量的遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很了不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說從繩文時代起這裡就有人居住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且附近曾經是一片海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈氣四處彌漫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鳥游同學  你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和從太古時代起存在於此處的靈魂對話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光明使者的細語
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑·彌·呼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不  我什麼都沒說  什麼都沒說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富樫君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鳥游同學在這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別害羞啦  快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再開你們玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧  小鳥游同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  小鳥游同學你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆真是太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經在交往了  沒必要這麼怕羞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我和勇太只是契約關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是是戀人契約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪王曲地腿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別在這種地方胡鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹生谷  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個房間的人要按規定時間去洗澡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說  你們一想到在戀愛就變得不自然了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們可是戀人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  仔細想想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙其實是不知道該怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中二病設定和戀愛之間似乎無法完美協調
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那該怎麼辦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能把她暫時拜託給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這樣好嗎  你們不想單獨在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話是這樣  但是大家都會注意到我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花她不太適應這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你也挺溫柔的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是溫柔嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩個人到底想怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  沒事我來就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係  反正我們都閑成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}無聊死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鯛魚襪子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36}注：鯛、靴下。冷笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這些  我關心的是漆黑烈焰使和主人之間的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小凸很激動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凸守一直都在意著他們是不是想要獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可他們到底想還是不想嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在家裡也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人老是偷偷摸摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺就像是我在礙事一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解你  我非常能理解你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dark·Flame  Master  &  GelZone  UNSAS'  Little  Sister！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我樟葉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樟葉你一定很喜歡哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道大家現在在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…什麼來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你們真的要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  還是別這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你已經有小鳥游同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一色他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一色他被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一色！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的只是搞錯了男浴室和女浴室而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一色…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣  只能採取B路線了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快點我們班的女生就要洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…丹生谷同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有嗎  丹生挺受歡迎的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊  沒有在交往的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那去年呢  跟某人交往過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼刨根問底的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年級的時候  丹生你跟富樫君關係很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯  還想著你們是不是在交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後跟小鳥游同學之間還是三角關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不好說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我這個戀愛大師看來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說三角關係了  丹生谷同學都沒跟人交往過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的女孩子還挺多的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來經驗豐富  實際上完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢  要說沒有也不完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初中的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是丹生你不是說你初中的時候是1200多歲來著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是有傳言說你現在偶爾也在網上這麼玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來晚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹生谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個一年級小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看這個反應  果然是丹生你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才  才  才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我沒有任何關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說都高中生了  怎麼可能去做這麼中二的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天還要早起  睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後在那女人旁邊鬼火慢慢地…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那麼嚇人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  而且比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更想知道富樫你們到哪一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼到哪一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還用問嗎  就是你跟小鳥游同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此  你們是從去年學園祭開始交往的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你們會知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一個月之後接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後總算去了約會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後在聖誕夜  你們倆…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現充去死！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挫骨揚灰！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有  你們別胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼時候做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那什麼…所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還…還沒做過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少來啦你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一個血氣方剛的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦痛致死吧  現充
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊  這時候還不說實話可是有點不地道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了這是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你把小鳥游同學給帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走廊裡還有老師在巡查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才窗戶上有可疑的光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像聽見了女孩子的呻吟聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別瞎說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南無阿彌陀佛  南無阿彌陀佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被發現了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  我使用了黑暗對魔防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人看不見我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是看錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人  為什麼不接電話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是跟漆黑烈焰使一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們倆按往常的感覺來的話  肯定什麼事都不會發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  這不是女生用的包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這房間裡的人還醒著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  老師來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人醒著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:17:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  那邊好像有奇怪的動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走只能趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我確實聽到了奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  可是誰都不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得在更裡面一些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊回房間  要是被發現了說不定會被送回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:18:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太跟我之間有一道屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是黑暗住民搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻礙我接近勇太的屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是精神攻擊的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已經沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不是逃避  也沒有躲著勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說你很害羞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的自由活動時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起逛逛吧  就我們兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見  六花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這究竟是戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是未滿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然依舊不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我感到有什麼正在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漸漸地  漸漸地萌芽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和六花迎來了那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  小鳥游同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是今天另有安排
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太把你的力量借給我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要封印它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只屬於我們兩個人的一天  開始了
